00:29:40,820 --> 00:29:42,880
The text introduces sheaf theory.

472
00:29:43,260 --> 00:29:47,400
It talks about stalks, germs, and cohomological obstructions.

473
00:29:47,760 --> 00:29:49,040
Let's please ground this.

